query.value:
SELECT
*
FROM ABC400FIL.BPSMSTDTL a
WHERE a.BPSMDCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}
AND a.BPSMDDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})  WITH UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.BPSMST a 
WHERE a.BPSMCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
and a.BPSMSDT >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  
AND a.BPSMSDT <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  with UR

select 
	BPSTRCD,
   BPSTRDS,
   BPSTLCD,
   BPSTDGD,
   BPSTDGA,
   BPSTRGD,
   BPSTRGA,
   BPSTFL1,
   BPSTFL2,
   BPSTSTX,
   BPSTOFF
from ABC400FIL.BPSTRC  with UR

SELECT 
CBADC, 
CBADS, 
CBADD, 
CBADT, 
CBADU, 
CBADI, 
CBADG, 
CBADA
FROM ABC400FIL.CBADTL a
WHERE CBADD > 20200101 AND a.CBADC in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR

SELECT CBATC, CBATS, CBATA, CBATT
FROM ABC400FIL.CBATXT a
WHERE a.CBATC  in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR

WHERE ctdclb in @{item().cbcpy_list}

FROM ABC400FIL.cbtnew a
WHERE ctnclb in @{item().cbcpy_list}

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CCADDRF a
WHERE a.ccacli in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT * FROM ABC400FIL.CCDUPDATRF 
WHERE DCUCDATE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart})  and   int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) with UR

select 
T1.CCEXTCLB,
T1.CCEXTMBR,
T1.CCEXTCPA,
T1.CCEXTCPP,
T1.CCEXTCPN,
T1.CCEXTEML,
T1.CCEXTGRP,
T1.CCEXTMB2,
T1.CCEXTLNG,
T1.CCEMPLOYR,
T1.CCOCCUPAT,
T1.CCSOURCE 
FROM ABC400FIL.ccfilext T1
WHERE T1.CCEXTCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  with UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CCFIL a
WHERE a.CCCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  with UR

SELECT 
CAST(t1.CDCLB as VARCHAR(6))  as CDCLB,
CAST(t1.CDMBR as VARCHAR(5))  as CDMBR,
CAST(t1.CDSEQ as VARCHAR(5))  as CDSEQ,
CAST(t1.CDDTE as VARCHAR(6))  as CDDTE,
CAST(t1.CDCEN as VARCHAR(2))  as CDCEN,
CAST(t1.CDMDE as VARCHAR(1))  as CDMDE,
CAST(t1.CDCDA as VARCHAR(9))  as CDCDA,
CAST(t1.CDTYP as VARCHAR(1))  as CDTYP,
CAST(t1.CDWAV as VARCHAR(1))  as CDWAV,
CAST(t1.CDCCTCODE as VARCHAR(10))  as CDCCTCODE,
CAST(t1.CDBFWDDATE as VARCHAR(9))  as CDBFWDDATE,
CAST(t1.CDFLAG1 as VARCHAR(1))  as CDFLAG1,
CAST(t1.CDFLAG2 as VARCHAR(1))  as CDFLAG2,
CAST(t1.CDFLAG3 as VARCHAR(1))  as CDFLAG3,
CAST(t1.CDFLAG4 as VARCHAR(1))  as CDFLAG4,
CAST(t1.CDFLAG5 as VARCHAR(1))  as CDFLAG5
FROM ABC400FIL.cdfil T1
where CDDTE >= 170101 AND CDDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND T1.CDCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.cgfilf a  with UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CGFIL a  with UR

SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CIFIL T1
INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV t3 on cisdt=MMDDYY
WHERE T3.The_date  BETWEEN TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') - CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
                   AND TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') + CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
AND CICLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  

UNION

SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CIFIL T1
INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV t3 on CITSD=MMDDYY
WHERE T3.The_date  BETWEEN TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') - CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
                       AND TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') + CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
AND CICLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 

UNION
--
--Future date 1/1/30 is a date that is used for presale clubs.”
SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CIFIL T1
WHERE cisdt=10130  
AND CICLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 

UNION
--
--Records that have CIBDT updated bit not CITSD and CISDT
SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CIFIL T1
INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV t3 on cibdt=MMDDYY
WHERE T3.The_date  BETWEEN TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') - CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
                       AND TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') + CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
AND CICLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}   

UNION
--
--Records that have CIDTE PANEL DATE --> Modified Date
SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.CIFIL T1
INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV t3 on CIDTE=MMDDYY
WHERE T3.The_date  BETWEEN TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') - CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
                       AND TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') + CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS 
AND CICLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 

UNION
-- Record that were copied because of Transfer
SELECT T2.*
FROM ABC400FIL.TFRATBL t1
JOIN ABC400FIL.CIFIL T2 on TRTOCLB=ciclb AND TRFRMEM=cimbr
WHERE T1.TRTRNENT  BETWEEN TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') - CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS
                       AND TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') + CAST('@{activity('GetRollingDays').output.firstRow.RollingDays}' AS INT) DAYS 
AND TRTOCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
WITH UR

SELECT distinct 
a.CLACUS#,
a.CLACLI#,
a.CLAGRP,
a.CLATRTP,
a.CLAPRTP,
a.CLARTN#,
CASE WHEN a.CLAACT# = '' THEN '' ELSE LPAD(right(rtrim(a.CLAACT#),4),8,'****')  END AS CLAACT#,
a.CLAACTP,
a.CLAWCDE,
a.CLADAMT,
a.CLACMPID,
a.CLASNAME,
a.CLADUNME,
a.CLADESC,
a.CLAEFDTE,
a.CLATRDTE,
a.CLAPRDTE
 from ABC400FIL.CLIACHFMF a
WHERE a.CLAEFDTE>=190101 AND a.CLAEFDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) and int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND CLACLI#  in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

*
FROM ABC400FIL.CLTLVLPFTP
where  PFCLIENT in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR
